Payment gateway plugin by CIELO Brazilian Credit Cards, for Marketpress.
Plugin de gateway de pagamento pela Cielo para MarketPress.Version: 1.0

== Description ==

Easiest then ever, is just upload plugin to plugins-gateway folder of marketpress and it will be ready.

You can see an online version working here: http://grupobms.culturalivre.com/
Note that this subdomain is without ssl. So if appears a security warning during the purchase navigation you can go ahead.
The theme that we used was this: http://www.marketpressthemes.com/ We did custom css for it and is at plugin folder. If you ganna use this theme you should to configure custom css at theme settings.

== Installation ==

1. Upload `cielo.php and other on the root folder` to the `/wp-content/plugins/marketpress/marketpress-includes/plugins-gateway/` directory
2. And it is ready. Now you should to contact cielo.com.br to affiliate and buy a https for the domain.

